{% comment %}
This helper is used to proxy assets to cloudflare.
* Heroku Proxy Box: draxe-image-proxy.herokuapp.com
* Cloudflare Subdomain pointed: shopify-cdn.draxe.com

KILL SWITCH: Remove the | remove and | replace portions to fallback to shopify's CDN if 

@author: TomFuertes@gmail.com
{% endcomment %}
{% if asset %}{{ asset | remove: 'https:' | remove: 'http:' | replace:'//cdn.shopify.com/','//shopify-cdn.draxe.com' }}{% endif %}